column5: Good morning everyone  Just curious if anyone knows the hours of operation ??? I'm sitting in the parking lot and thy are closed right now ... Just wondering if I should wait around or are they closed for the day !  Thanks
I guess by now you know they are open they are closed on Sundays
It wouldn't have surprised me if they were closed today; they had a ton of water leaks through the roof yesterday. I'm holding out for a flood sale... 80% off all water damaged fishing tackle!!!
Lol Brian that would be great LMK when it's on.
It would be pretty sad to see water leaks damaging FISHING tackle
"Water damaged fishing tackle?" No i know why i buy tackle and keep it safe and clean in my bags...lol
